meta.name: os-family-db

signature.order_key: Strict order of TCP options after NOP compression (e.g., 'MSS,SACK,TS,WS')
signature.has_ts: Whether TCP timestamps option is present (boolean)
signature.has_sack: Whether TCP SACK permitted option is present (boolean)
signature.has_ws: Whether TCP window scale option is present (boolean)

meta.confidence_note: Confidence is approximated by majority share and the number of present TCP option features. In practice, use a threshold (e.g., >= 0.75) to make a definitive classification; otherwise, mark as unknown.
